    <title>Women and Girls contributor: Sandra Prüfer</title>
    <description>Sandra Prüfer is a Bonn-based freelance writer and digital storytelling enthusiast with more than two decades of experience in international reporting, non-profit and corporate communications. She has reported extensively in print and television on politics, development, environment and health issues, with a focus on questions of climate change, gender equality and social justice. Follow her on Twitter at @spruefer.
</description>
